snippet.title: Mission Zero | Character Trailer: Vanessa
snippet.description:
As the manager of the cleaning robots, elegant「Vanessa」can't accept any filth. In her eyes, members of Sirius from the underground city, are something like incomparably dirty bacteria.
"It's better to clean up the Sirius as soon as possible!" 
------------------------------------
The Technical Test will start on July 8th. Please follow us to get the first-hand information! 
- Pre-register now: https://www.missionzero.game/
- Discord: https://discord.gg/tQZTBYwgRC
- Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Missionzerog...
